<p>Students in residence are advised to label any edible products appropriately and are not permitted to store them in shared residence community spaces.</p> 
<p>Consequences for any inappropriate behaviour on campus and in residences related to the use of alcohol/drugs may be addressed through the<a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/calendar/2018-2019/policies-and-procedures/rights-conduct/codes-of-conduct/"> Student Code of Non-Academic Conduct (Policy 61)</a>.</p> 
