<p><strong>The&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/hr/work-life/wellbeing-at-work/efap/">Employee and Family Assistance Program (EFAP)</a></strong>&nbsp;is a confidential and voluntary support service that can help you solve all kinds of problems and challenges in your life, including substance abuse and addiction. The program is administered by Shepell and services are entirely anonymous. Neither HR nor supervisors are privy to information regarding who has accessed the program.</p>
    





