<h2>
	
    Managing Misconduct
    
	
</h2>


</div>

				

				
				<div class="resAccordion section">
























 


<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <div class="panel-group accordion background-hidden" id="d3fada3f-2f31-47fa-92b2-e23bd6a71368" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">
			
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <div class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1536264078302-what-do-i-do-if-i-see-someone-smoking-or-vaping-cannabis-on-campus-" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#d3fada3f-2f31-47fa-92b2-e23bd6a71368" href="#accordion-content-1536264078302-what-do-i-do-if-i-see-someone-smoking-or-vaping-cannabis-on-campus-" aria-controls="accordion-content-1536264078302-what-do-i-do-if-i-see-someone-smoking-or-vaping-cannabis-on-campus-" aria-expanded="false">
                            What do I do if I see someone smoking or vaping cannabis on campus?
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1536264078302-what-do-i-do-if-i-see-someone-smoking-or-vaping-cannabis-on-campus-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1536264078302-what-do-i-do-if-i-see-someone-smoking-or-vaping-cannabis-on-campus-">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1536264078302 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="a5210c5e-d138-448a-905e-306b58c217db" >

    <p>Ryerson's approach to managing cannabis on campus focuses on education and awareness. Security is on campus 24/7, and will ensure that community members are aware of and following the rules.</p> 
<p>Everyone on campus will be expected to abide by all provincial regulations regarding recreational cannabis&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ontario.ca/page/cannabis-legalization#section-6">cultivation<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ontario.ca/page/cannabis-legalization#section-4">sale<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ontario.ca/page/cannabis-legalization#section-5">possession<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ontario.ca/page/cannabis-legalization#section-2">use<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a>.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p>
    





</div>
